Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.69,0:01:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我站住  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那堆垃圾带出去扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that pile of filth out with you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.39,0:01:24.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  不可以这么说章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:24.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, you shouldn't talk about Squidward like that
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说的是这个垃圾  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He means this filth, you loon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.06,0:01:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去扔垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taking out the trash
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.57,0:01:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾桶上的字句
