Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,线虫也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nematodes are people, too
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些线虫可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those nematodes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有句还没写完的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's one somebody didn't finish
