Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥闻起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward smells
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这句写的啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this one?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs is a
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs is a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168,212)}老    螃    蟹    是
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是用这张臭嘴来亲你妈的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you kiss your mother with that mouth?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.32,0:02:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候会亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.10,0:02:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but not
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.10,0:02:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最近没亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,recently
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  收垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, garbage man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.83,0:02:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你知道这几个字什么意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, do you know what this word means?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.66,0:02:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是你那个挥汗如雨的红色老板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the red, sweaty guy you work for?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这几个字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh, not that word
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168,212)}老    螃    蟹    是
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这几个字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That word
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该知道是什么意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I know what that means
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.10,0:02:34.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是用来增强语气的语气词
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:34.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's one of those sentence enhancers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,增强语气的语气词
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sentence enhancers?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要讲话花俏就可以用上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You use them when you want to talk fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只要加到你想讲的话里面然后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just sprinkle it over anything you say and
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wham-o
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.98,0:02:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你讲的话就会变得辛辣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got yourself a spicy sentence sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.12,0:02:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lovely
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错  你说是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,day we're having, isn't it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.12,0:02:58.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊没错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:58.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, yes, it is, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.13,0:02:58.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:02:58.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气可真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,day is particularly
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lovely
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.35,0:03:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right you are, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.49,0:03:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这辛辣的话讲的我嘴唇都麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My lips are tingling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the spiciness of this conversation
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.09,0:03:16.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的也麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine, too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一笑就麻了
