Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, how the
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.61,0:03:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,good, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是家餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought this was a restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是嘴臭大会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not a gutter-mouth convention
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顾客们请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, customers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今日特餐是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's special is a
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  配以油腻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty served in a greasy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酱料  肉饼煎至
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sauce and grilled to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恰到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,perfection
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也别忘了来点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, don't forget to ask us to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fries
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.79,0:04:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be our
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.18,0:04:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.18,0:04:06.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:06.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How the
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.01,0:04:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错  是不是啊章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,day, isn't it, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.23,0:04:15.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那人明明很有才  完全没必要嘴臭的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:15.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy's talented, he doesn't have to work blue
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱们到更适合家庭的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere more family oriented
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不会来这吃东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm never eating here again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那俩到处嘴臭的臭鱼烂虾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those foul-mouthed bottom feeders
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(676,304)}最大容量
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人都走光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's empty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体成员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hands on deck
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,封住大门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Batten the front doors
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加固收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brace the cash register
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放出快乐食品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Break out the happy snacks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.06,0:04:43.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那些来花钱的漂亮客人都哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:43.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where have all me beautiful paying customers gone?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,显然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Apparently
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那两个嘴臭兄弟刚学到了个新词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the two barnacle-mouth brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just learned a new word
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.89,0:04:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后海绵宝宝用话筒到处说这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and SpongeBob just said it over the intercom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那词是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what was it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说了啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.06,0:04:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.27,0:04:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he said
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  还有你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and friend
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我出列
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Front and center
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要以你们言语不当为由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I ought to make the two of you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你们两个粉刷蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,paint the Krusty Krab for using such language
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是拿那些来加强语气而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we were only using our sentence enhancers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  这样讲话会花俏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's fancy talk
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那话一点都不花俏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There ain't nothing fancy about that word
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就是这话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, that one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在不准说这话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, quit saying that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是脏话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a bad word
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad word?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, siree
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个是11号脏话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's bad word number 11
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  你们绝对不能讲的脏话有13个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, there are 13 bad words you should never use
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是说只有7个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean there are only seven?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是水手才会只有7个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not if you're a sailor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,13个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,13
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.26,0:05:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bad words
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你们向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to promise me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不会再讲那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll never use that word again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们保证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We promise
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴蟹老板告诉我们说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure am glad Mr. Krabs told us
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们讲的那话是脏话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that word we were using was a bad word
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我也高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们这样有格调又见多识广的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because classy sophisticates like us
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不应该用粗话来玷污我们的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,should not stain our lips with cursing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, verily
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来玩一盘好玩益智的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's play a nice, wholesome game of
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鳗梯棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eels and Escalators
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.64,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 鳗梯棋：改自蛇梯棋 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  我最爱玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, my favorite
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇出好手气  小蜗还要新鞋子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary needs a new pair of shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鳗鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eels
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可惜了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得骑鳗鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to ride the eel
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Escalators
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up, up, up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Escalators
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是鳗鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eels again
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.25,0:06:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Escalators
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Escalators
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鳗鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eels?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.85,0:06:58.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Es-kee-lators
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是你最后的机会了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is your last chance, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,582)}你输了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你又掷出鳗鱼来  你就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you get eels again, you lose
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Escalators
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Escalators
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鳗鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eels
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说了11号脏话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said number 11
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.05,0:07:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要理解我啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to understand, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来是要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was trying
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I meant to say was
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某些话就这么顺口而出了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some things just slip out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要理解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to understand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.70,0:07:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别去啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  拜托你别告状
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, no, please don't tell
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.05,0:07:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you said
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要向蟹老板告你的状了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm going to tell Mr. Krabs on you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也得等我先说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not if I tell first
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以跑得比你快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can run faster than you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们蟹堡王再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:03.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1064,184)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,384)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板蟹老板蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, Mr. Krabs, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥事啥事啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, what, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星派大星派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, Patrick, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了咋了咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说了他说了他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said, he said, he said
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有话快说  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out with it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟派大星本来在玩鳗梯棋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and Patrick were playing Eels and Escalators
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一直升上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he was going up-up-up
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只能骑鳗鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I had to ride the eel
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱俩狂奔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then we ran
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星就说出来了某些话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Patrick said some things
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he said
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.32,0:08:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是他说了你说的我们不该说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just say he said a certain word
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you said he shouldn't say
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而这话刚好就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this particular word happens to be
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的我们不该说的13句话中的11号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,word number 11 in a list of 13 words
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you said shouldn't be said
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.91,0:08:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that part about the
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who now?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板蟹老板蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, Mr. Krabs, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说了你说的我们不该说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said that word you said we shouldn't say
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在要松开你们的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm going to let go of your lips
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等松开完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when I do
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.50,0:08:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你们冷静说出你们想跟我说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to calmly tell me what youse need to tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.06,0:09:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有没有听错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do my ears deceive me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该要为此羞耻才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two should be ashamed
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扔垃圾时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to take out the trash
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个要学点教训
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two need to be taught a lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来还以为我都说清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I made it clear
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.88,0:09:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.37,0:09:26.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是不准说11号或者任何一号脏话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:26.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,never use number 11 or any of the 13 bad words
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个现在在这好好给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, the both of youse wait right here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可能会被打40大鞭子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll probably get 40 lashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1010,920)}睫 毛
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is right
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种话根本没有说出口的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no need for words like that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.79,0:09:49.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也对不起  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:49.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, too, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来发誓  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's make a vow, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.77,0:09:54.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从今天起我们一句脏话都不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From this day forth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a foul word shall never pass our lips
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要当好市民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will be good citizens
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟蟹老板一样的好市民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like good old Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Agreed
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  你们两个嘴臭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you two foul mouths
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了惩罚你们乱讲脏话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As punishment for fouling the air
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,污染了蟹堡王的大好气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in me restaurant with your foul words
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要给蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're going to give the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全粉刷一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a fresh coat of paint
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从上到下都要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from top to bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.50,0:10:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.26,0:10:14.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:14.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,foot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼才往马路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,genius put a
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rock in a
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.65,0:10:18.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:18.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,path
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道我脚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I got a
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要踩这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,foot here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五六七
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five, six, seven
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.27,0:10:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and with a side of
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整个就一堆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a heaping helping of
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一整船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a boatload of
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,横行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,crabbing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十三个都齐了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's all 13, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要找你妈告状  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to tell your mom, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你们不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, please
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要跟我妈讲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not my mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  求你们不要跟我妈说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, please don't tell me mother
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.52,0:10:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她的小心脏会遭不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think her little old heart can take it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hello there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹妈妈  他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama Krabs, he said
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.98,0:11:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又再说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then he said
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.97,0:11:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he said
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,again and said
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再然后他就扯着嗓子大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then he screamed at the top of his voice
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.31,0:11:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹妈妈  他根本不放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Krabs, he didn't care
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.85,0:11:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直就是一股
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such a stream of
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从前从来就没有听过这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have never heard in my days
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可怜的小心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My poor, old heart
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dear mother
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.89,0:11:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那两个嘴臭的对你都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have these foul-mouthed heathens done to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个应该感到羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two should be ashamed
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们居然出口成脏  让个老太太昏倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Making an old lady faint with your sailor talk
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都应该感到羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should all be ashamed
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们要像水手那样出口成脏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if you're going to talk like sailors
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们就得像水手那样好好干活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you're going to work like sailors
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些小捣蛋可以来领柠檬水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you scalawags have earned a glass of lemonade
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,foot
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.99,0:12:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,声音是老头简金斯跟他那辆破车发的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's old man Jenkins and his jalopy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹太太好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Mrs. K
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.50,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,347)}不知名的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(324,468)\frz17.8}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:23.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.8\pos(298,396)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.8\pos(396,316)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.8\pos(316,354)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.8\pos(484,692)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,604)}成人学习中心
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我老想有这么一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How I have dreamed of this day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.64,0:12:34.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  艺术教授
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:34.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tentacles, Professor of Art
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.53,0:12:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是献给裤头村居民们的大好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a marvelous opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the people of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.13,0:12:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你们那群没事干的家庭主妇都带来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring me your huddled masses of bored housewives
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.82,0:12:45.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把她们塑造成我心中的大好形象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:45.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I will shape them in my image
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会名垂青史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go down in history
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.03,0:12:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终有一天  会有座挂着我名字的展厅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someday, there will be a wing with my name on it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.00,0:12:58.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建在全世界所有博物馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:58.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in all the museums of the world
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  你这是在活动中心教艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude, you're teaching art at the rec center
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.91,0:13:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没文化的垃圾废物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Uncultured trash urchin
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.93,0:13:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该让同学们进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to let the class in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能再让他们继续等下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, don't want to keep them waiting any longer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来上艺术课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to art class
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是烹饪课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this "Cooking"?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也是来上这节艺术课的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you taking this art class, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.22,0:13:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来上艺术课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In art class
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都别走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是烹饪课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是在逗我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你一起来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and me in school together
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那老师在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, where's the teacher?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在你眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're looking at him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are the "Teacher"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在我这学生眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my "Pupil"?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根本不是艺术课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't art class
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直就是天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's heaven
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.58,0:13:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带点天堂走  开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab a little piece of heaven and let's get on with it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了  章鱼哥老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.19,0:13:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你是想当个艺术家吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you want to be an artist, eh, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.48,0:14:00.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,艺术可不全是嬉耍打闹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:00.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, art is not all fun and games
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是勤奋苦干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a lot of hard work
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  跟我念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, repeat after me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有才华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no talent
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有才华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no talent
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.28,0:14:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥老师满腹才华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tentacles has all the talent
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥老师满腹才华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tentacles has all the talent
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有幸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'm lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许可以沾点章鱼哥老师的才华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some of Mr. Tentacles' talent may rub off on me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.39,0:14:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有幸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'm lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.70,0:14:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才华老师的章鱼触手可以沾我艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Talent will rub his tentacles on my art
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.14,0:14:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你说你先前没练过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since you're telling me you have no prior training
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就从零开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll have to start from square one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.94,0:14:40.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可以说是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:40.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or should I say
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从圆开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,circle one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我教得太快了吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I going too fast for you, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.96,0:14:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个行不  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's this, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How the
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美的圆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A perfect circle?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再画一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看你画的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show your process
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先画出来这个脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, I draw this head
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后再擦掉一点点细节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I erased some of the more detailed features
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one, two, three
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画了个圆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a circle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thingy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.23,0:15:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管什么圆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the circles
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lookey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我跟你在玩跳山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you and me playing leapfrog
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面那个是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's you on the bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳山羊跟艺术半毛钱关系都没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is nothing artistic about leapfrog
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这又是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing now?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个叫做  小碎屑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call it rippy bits
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿一堆碎纸屑来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You take a bunch of old, ripped-up paper
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画出来幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and make a new picture out of it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回你在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on top
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底还学不学艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to learn art or not?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Squidward--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会认真听的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll listen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我全神贯注
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pay close attention
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着大理石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at your marble
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,构思出它内在的雕塑的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Visualize the sculpture within
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再轻轻地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then gently
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个怎么样  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's this, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.23,0:16:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根本算不上雕塑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't a sculpture
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要雕出好雕塑就要花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A good sculpture takes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more time
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能一下子就马上雕好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't just sculpt willy-nilly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要照着书本上的做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to go by the book
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(372,218)}艺术的规矩
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着规矩去做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,follow the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则你就不可能越过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you'll never get past
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种业余阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,amateur hour here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且你鼻子也雕错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, you got the nose wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.72,0:16:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's art
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都明摆着了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没想过得那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would have never thought of that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来这学艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I came here to learn
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.47,0:16:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却傲慢地顶撞了你的课
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I arrogantly shunned your lessons
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没办法成为像你一样伟大的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never be a great artist like you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不配让你来教我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve your tutoring
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不配出现在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve to be in your presence
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.07,0:16:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我甚至都不配用你的门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even deserve to use your doors
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只配这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I did deserve that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I deserved that, too
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也只配这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I deserve this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(396,298)}垃圾场
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,午安  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.93,0:17:10.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  下课了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:10.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, class is dismissed
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.71,0:17:11.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:11.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're too late
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真抱歉  我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon, but I'd forgotten my manners
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫钱袋蒙蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is Monty P. Moneybags
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界知名的艺术收藏家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The world-famous art collector?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独一无二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The one and only
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来这有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在做大采购
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on a shopping spree
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我新开的博物馆买艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,buying art for my new museum
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不用再去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your search is over
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正是裤头村最伟大的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Bikini Bottom's greatest artiste
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.19,0:17:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个叫做  章鱼哥的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call this one Squidward in Repose
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.57,0:17:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,觉得这玩意跟我的其他藏品会不搭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't think that will fit in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the other pieces in my collection
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我那都是艺术藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because it's an art collection
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.63,0:17:49.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:49.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.83,0:17:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个叫做  大胆创造
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call it Bold and Brash
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该得叫  垃圾创造
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More like Belongs in the Trash
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肯定是忘了清理掉这份了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have missed that one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怕是得要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should be
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.27,0:18:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.31,0:18:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天使一样的形体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Angelic form
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精妙无比的细节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing detail
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恰到好处的和谐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect censorship
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.24,0:18:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是天才的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the work of a true genius
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这啥玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是唯一的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the only flaw
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's more like it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.67,0:18:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须要找到做出这个的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I simply must find the artist responsible
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会拥有名声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He shall have fame
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.83,0:18:38.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:38.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fame
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,财富
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fortune
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.57,0:18:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,财富
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fortune
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.03,0:18:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,期望得到的任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything his heart desires
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我雕出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm responsible
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能预见到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can see it now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.70,0:18:56.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你名字会挂进全世界最著名的博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:56.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your name in the world's most prestigious museums
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.51,0:19:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让你  名垂千古
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:19:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am going to make you immortal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.09,0:19:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我把这个抬到车上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,help me get this in the car
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要来人帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could use a little help
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My fame
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My fortune
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hair
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可真是有点倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a bit of bad luck right there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.98,0:19:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对你这种伟大的艺术家应当不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this shouldn't be a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for an artist of your magnitude
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以马上再雕另外一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can whip up another one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.97,0:19:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说  你别传出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, between you and me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发挥最佳的作品可不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this isn't my best work
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你明天过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come back tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.98,0:19:37.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时候我保证有东西能让你惊掉袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll have something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that will really knock your socks off
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说  我没穿袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Between you and me, I'm not wearing socks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  没穿袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no socks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得找到海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to find SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(366,814)}垃圾场
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你走吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我配不上你的一片好心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve your kindness
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.66,0:20:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我决定要再给你一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have decided to give you another chance
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.90,0:20:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有我这样的良师在  一切皆有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, with a great teacher like me, anything is possible
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看我了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't look at my shame
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这两只手就不能用来创造
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These hands weren't meant to create
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.62,0:20:19.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:19.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They only destroy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.63,0:20:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都没法直视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't look at them
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.03,0:20:31.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经有双可爱的小黄手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:31.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got yourself a pair of yellow dandies here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.62,0:20:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有我帮忙  就会变成创造美的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and with my help, we'll turn them into tools of beauty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.60,0:20:41.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:41.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.19,0:20:43.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:43.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, look
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是大胆创造
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's old Bold and Brash
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做你之前做过的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just do what you did before
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me help
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们再来从圆开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the circle again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, but
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what about the head
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有擦掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the erasing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the, the
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意没写在书上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That stuff's not in the book
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1142,542)}艺术的规矩
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.84,0:21:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意也没写在书上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not in the book either
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要管什么书了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget about the book
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.90,0:21:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可真是乱  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all this mess, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.05,0:21:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看到这些小纸片想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do all these little bits of paper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make you want to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会  这个我会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I know this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.65,0:21:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会  快成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I think I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快了快了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go and yes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接来弄大理石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just move on to the marble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.04,0:22:02.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,艺术家首先要专心构思作品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, an artist must concentrate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:02.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and visualize his concept
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得抱大理石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to embrace the marble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.83,0:22:06.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:06.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得闻大理石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to sniff the marble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.70,0:22:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得舔大理石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to lick the marble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得洗大理石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to wash the marble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.60,0:22:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得约大理石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to date the marble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得变大理石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to be the marble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.33,0:22:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.48,0:22:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到大理石内在的雕塑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have seen the sculpture within
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.44,0:22:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.49,0:22:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了这工具  我就要诞生出艺术了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With this tool, I shall give birth to art
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.74,0:22:32.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:32.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But one more thing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.16,0:22:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这是艺术了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's art
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.38,0:22:41.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:41.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you think, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽心欣赏一小会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take it all in for a moment
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.42,0:22:47.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沉浸其中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:47.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let it soak in
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.24,0:23:10.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像我的艺术成就
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:10.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like the excitement of my artistic triumph
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.11,0:23:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让章鱼哥兴奋过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is too much for Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.53,0:23:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行吧  回垃圾场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, back to the dump
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.54,0:23:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾场  垃圾场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the dump, to the dump
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.33,0:23:17.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾场场场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:17.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the dump, dump, dump
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.04,0:23:17.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾场  垃圾场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:17.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the dump, to the dump
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.83,0:23:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾场场场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the dump, dump, dump
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.67,0:23:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来这
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here for the
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.31,0:23:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is responsible for this?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这些全是他干的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As of now, it's his responsibility
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.97,0:23:34.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:34.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day to you, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.81,0:23:42.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是史上最伟大的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:42.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, sir, are the greatest artist who ever lived
